-- Altran to Rework Management Structure, Announce Acquisitions, Echos Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-06-29T04:43:36Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/altran-to-rework-management-structure-announce-acquisitions-echos-says.html

          
          
             Altran SA will announce a new
management structure at its shareholders meeting today, Les
Echos reported, citing Chairman Yves De Chaisemartin.  
 The company will appoint an executive with global
responsibility for each of its activities, Les Echos said.
Altran also has three acquisitions to be announced in the
future, according to the newspaper.  
          
          


  


        